biz.gabrys.lesscss.extended.compiler.cache

Class FullCacheAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • biz.gabrys.lesscss.extended.compiler.cache.FullCacheAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CompilationDateCache, CompiledCodeCache, FullCache, SourceCodeCache, SourceImportsCache, SourceModificationDateCache

    public class FullCacheAdapter
extends Object
implements FullCache
    Allows you to create an instance of FullCache which delegates execution of each method to concrete caches.
    Since:
    1.0
